Package io.proximax.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Constants
    This class specifies the constants used by this SDK
    DataInfoModel
    This model class defines the details of a data
    ProximaxDataModel
    This model class represents the details of an uploaded data

    The following are its fields: digest - the computed digest for the data (already encrypted data by privacy strategy) dataHash - the data hash to access the data (already encrypted data by privacy strategy) description - a description of the data metadata - an additional metadata for the data timestamp - the timestamp when the upload occurred name - the name for the data (file name by default if a file upload) contentType - the content type of the data (detected if none specified)
    ProximaxMessagePayloadModel
    This model class represents the transaction message
